      "text": [
        " - «صَلَّى فِي مَسْجِدِ اَلْخَيْفِ سَبْعُمِائَةِ نَبِيٍّ."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.688 - As for the Mosque of Al-Khayf in Mina, it has been narrated by Jabir from Imam Muhammad ibn Ali Al-Baqir (as) that He said:\n\"Seven hundred prophets prayed in the Mosque of al-Khayf.\""
        ]
